Dialogue: 1,0:00:02.31,0:00:03.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.31,0:00:03.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.56,0:00:07.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:07.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.02,0:00:09.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:09.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.20,0:00:15.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:15.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.99,0:00:18.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:18.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.99,0:00:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.21,0:00:23.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:23.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.96,0:00:26.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:26.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.29,0:00:27.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:27.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.46,0:00:28.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:28.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.09,0:00:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
