Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.12,0:01:02.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该睡觉了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:02.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for bed, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.54,0:01:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.34,0:01:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俗话说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what they say
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好奇心害死蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,curiosity salted the snail
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.30,0:01:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别被迷了眼  你这小蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mind your wandering eye, you little mollusk
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.76,0:01:19.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你做个好梦  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:19.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet dreams, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.05,0:01:53.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:53.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还没有驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have a driver's license
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:57.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(741.311,205)}裤头村驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:57.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(925.878,969.001)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.51,0:02:01.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:01.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My driver's license
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我照片拍得可真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure take a good picture
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:08.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(755.507,720.999)}道路尽头
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.94,0:02:09.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:09.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.35,0:02:10.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道就留胡子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:10.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should have grown a moustache
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.03,0:02:17.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么能忘掉最重要的交规
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how could I have forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the most important rule of driving?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要系好安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always wear your seatbelt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(341.754,697.001)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里可以看到蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can see the Krusty Krab from here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, look
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.33,0:02:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我终于有驾照了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finally got my driver's license
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.70,0:02:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就算做梦也不能领驾照  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not even in your dreams, Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.29,0:02:34.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:34.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that me?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.01,0:02:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是这个是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or is this me?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.51,0:02:41.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还在做梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:41.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I still dreaming?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.31,0:02:46.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个肯定是小蜗的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:46.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This must be Gary's dream
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要进去看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get a closer look
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这些书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all these books
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道小蜗在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Gary is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问一下  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有没有看见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you seen
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.74,0:03:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你竟敢侵犯我纯洁的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How dare you invade the sanctity of my dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你原来会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can talk
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.79,0:03:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尘世的限制无法束缚梦中的个体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In dreams, one is not tethered by earthly limitations
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长久以来  人们认为梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For ages, dreams have been thought of
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是通向另一个世界的窗口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as windows to another realm
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,梦境甚完美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Let me not mar that perfect dream
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,莫让晨曦玷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"by an auroral stain
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.89,0:03:28.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每夜皆修整
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:28.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"but so adjust my daily night
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方能再出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that it may come again"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是艾米莉迪金森写的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Emily Dickinson wrote that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.06,0:03:33.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:33.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这首你应该比较熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's one you might know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:46.41,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 爱德华·利尔所作的打油诗 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前有个秘鲁人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"There once was a man from Peru
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,梦见吃鞋入了神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"who dreamed he was eating his shoe
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,半夜梦中惊坐起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"He woke with a fright in the middle of the night
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.24,0:03:46.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发现梦居然成真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:46.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to find that his dream had come true"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你好聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Gary, you sure are smart
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你以为我壳里都是装热气的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you think my shell was full of hot air?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢你的教导  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for the info, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要回到我自己的梦里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to my own dream now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.29,0:03:58.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别被迷了眼  你这小海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:58.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beware of your wandering eye, you little poriferan
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道派大星在做什么梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Patrick's dreaming
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忍不住就是要看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't resist
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  这是个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, Patrick, this is a dream
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想做什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can do anything you want
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.78,0:04:26.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:26.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean anything
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以变成摩天大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can turn into a skyscraper
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,变高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以变出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can make
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一百万个我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a million of me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.46,0:04:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要到别人的梦里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to a different dream
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.01,0:04:45.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:45.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shoot
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只剩那个两毛五硬币了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was my last quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回肯定会特别的好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be good
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.62,0:05:14.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:14.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.63,0:05:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么不吹下去了  莫章特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do you stop playing, Wolfgang Amadeus Tentacles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:23.80,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自奥地利作曲家莫扎特 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Highness
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没有命令过你要停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have not instructed you to stop
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我吹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, play
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.81,0:05:43.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再跟我讲点那个秘鲁人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:43.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do tell me the one about the man from Peru again
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.07,0:05:47.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:47.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,, Bob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.53,0:05:52.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朕是来这聆听美妙乐曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:52.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I came here to hear beautiful music
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.03,0:05:55.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是听不到  你的头就跟它一个下场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:55.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I don't get my wish, it'll be your head
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.13,0:06:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.13,0:06:03.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:03.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,way
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我求你了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准耍花招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No tricks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相信我吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trust me, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.44,0:06:29.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为何停止吹奏那美妙的音乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:29.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why have you stopped playing that wonderful music?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其仙乐动我心脾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His music touches me ever so
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热泪盈眶青衫湿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l fear that my tears might stain my petticoat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(593.252,855)}美食车
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.97,0:06:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这发出曼妙乐声的是何种乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this instrument
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that produces such lovely sound?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到珊迪家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm at Sandy's
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.87,0:07:15.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着就挺酷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:15.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This looks neat
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.83,0:07:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  什么风把你给吹来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, what brings you here?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.63,0:07:23.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:23.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.13,0:07:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是在114000英尺的高空自由落体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we're free-falling from 114,000 feet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要降落到那个很小的目标点上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we're going to land on that itty-bitty target
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有点危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This seems kind of dangerous
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要有个降落伞就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not as long as you got a big, old parachute
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是鞋子  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not "pair of shoes," SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:40.02,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 引号内容互相谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是降落伞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"para-chute"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.02,0:07:40.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:40.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是鹦鹉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a "parakeet"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.98,0:07:44.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是降落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:44.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,para
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(931.962,845.001)}蛤蜊粪
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.44,0:07:46.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:46.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Medic
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要再去捣乱别人的梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more messing with people's dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  原来这是你的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, this is your dream
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚好赶上我的茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just in time for the tea party
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我是在找你爸的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was looking for your dad's dream
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.81,0:08:25.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:25.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's next door
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.69,0:08:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,男生就是不懂茶会有多优雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:27.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boys don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the sophistication of tea parties
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  毛绒玩具先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Mr. Stuffy?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.49,0:08:36.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板的梦肯定会更阳刚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:36.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet Mr. Krabs' dream will be more robust
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于逮到你了  滑头恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got you now, you slippery demon
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟我斗的劲儿还挺大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're putting up a good fight
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大得很哪你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you doing, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在扒海神王的口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm picking Neptune's pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就那个冰冷坚硬  翻来覆去的现金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'm talking about cold, hard, flipping cash
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是大白钱莫比刀乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the mighty Moby dollar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.64,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自白鲸莫比·迪克 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.64,0:08:59.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见它了没  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:08:59.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you see her, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我逮到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got her
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here she comes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它喷钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thar she blows
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pennies
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用管这点零钱了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind the small change, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.98,0:09:08.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿网来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:08.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get the net
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了错了错了  是捕钱网
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no, the money net
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在我屁股口袋里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's in me back pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你长小胡子的样子可真帅  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look real good with a moustache, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(674.379,267.001)}裤头村驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1153.037,841.001)}蟹老板
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那东西不关你事  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind that, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.24,0:09:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把网准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready the net
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,网准备好了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Net ready, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.79,0:09:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我终于抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I finally did it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别把它给放走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't let it go
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  快抓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快抓  快抓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get it, get it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.88,0:09:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这事一定会名垂野史的对吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This'll make a great fish story, eh, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're fired
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(749.042,920)}发 射
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(938.046,861.001)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板梦见裤头村了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton's dreaming about Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zap
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zap
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zap
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zap
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:23.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(449.247,641)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.01,0:10:20.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看啊  是蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:20.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, look, it's the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡之家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,home of the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我踩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crush
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我舔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick, lick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就不是什么正经梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't a dream
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就一噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.23,0:10:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.78,0:10:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来  小猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, kitty, kitty, kitty
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我护住你了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got you, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快藏好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peekaboo
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脚来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here comes my foot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.71,0:10:49.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:49.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来他抓住重点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l think he's got the point
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.30,0:11:04.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该是有得解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:04.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I've got some explaining to do, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.01,0:11:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别别别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别踩脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not the face
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.48,0:11:18.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好玩归好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was fun and all
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过还是回自己的梦乡里好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's good to be back in my own dream cloud
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想把我怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.04,0:11:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别别别别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都穿睡衣来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are y'all doing in your pajamas?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是在办睡衣派对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are we having a slumber party?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是  我们没在办睡衣派对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, we are not having a slumber party
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行行好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do us all a favor, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别来搞我们的梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and stay out of our dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚远点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a hike
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白天跟你一起还不够受的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't we get enough of you during the day?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁有两毛五硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does anyone have a quarter?
