Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在下蟹黄堡雨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's raining Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃点宵夜然后再回去睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A quick midnight snack, and then it's back to bed
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.91,0:12:52.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1194.523,830.25)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好睡吧  我的小天使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sleep tight, my little angel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:00.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1089.515,684)}海花生酱
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.42,0:13:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海花生酱配水母酱三明治吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a sea-nut butter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and jellyfish jelly sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最能助眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to help you get to sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fridge
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.99,0:14:13.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我感觉不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:13.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, I don't feel like myself
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别傻了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没得感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get colds
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得的是肥皂泡病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get the suds
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.34,0:14:25.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得肥皂泡病就会有泡泡冒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:25.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I had the suds, I'd have bubbles coming out of me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不能得肥皂泡病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't get the suds
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为这样会害我误工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because then I'll have to miss work
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放屁  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是喜欢这样穿内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l like wearing my underwear like this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.49,0:14:48.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:48.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not sick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.78,0:14:49.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:49.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to work
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(396.552,520)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  蟹黄堡怎么做得这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what's holding up those patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就好  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right away, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你脸色可是苍白得不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're paler than a baby sea horse
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.00,0:15:06.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肥皂泡病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:06.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The suds?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要的蟹黄堡来了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's that patty you wanted, Mr. Krabs, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你病得不能再上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, SpongeBob, you're too sick to work
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.85,0:15:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没事  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm okay, honest
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  快回家休息去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, now go home and get some rest
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是在针对你  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing personal, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不能让你把喷嚏打在食物上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just can't have you sneezing all over my food
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.70,0:15:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我逗谁呢  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who am I kidding, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.09,0:15:51.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得肥皂泡病了  毫无疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:51.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got the suds, no doubt about it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好先处理好  免得病情失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l better take care of this before it gets out of hand
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.61,0:16:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.73,0:16:07.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  我病了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:07.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, I'm sick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能送我去看医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you escort me to the doctor's?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.65,0:16:15.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到你那会快得不得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'll be there faster than a barefoot jackrabbit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on a hot greasy griddle in the middle of August
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Sandy, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.79,0:16:24.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:24.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是去滑雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going skiing?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我病了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sick, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.80,0:16:30.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:30.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't go
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.22,0:16:35.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认识的一个人认识的一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:35.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know a guy who knows a guy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前去看过一次医生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who went to the doctor once
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门诊部可是超级可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the doctor's office is a horrible, horrible place
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定没肥皂泡病可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It can't be as horrible as the suds
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的很可怕  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先  他们会让你坐进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, first they make you sit in the
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,候诊室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,waiting room
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这段可怕吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that the horrible part, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  之后更可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it gets worse
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.86,0:16:58.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们会让你看旧杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:58.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They make you read old magazines
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.45,0:17:03.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后医生就会拿出听诊器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:03.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then the doctor pulls out his stethoscope
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个设备特别邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a device so sinister
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.25,0:17:12.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又特别冰冷  一旦触碰到你的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:12.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so icy cold, when it touches your bare flesh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.71,0:17:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要听诊器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No stethoscope
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.10,0:17:18.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要医生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:18.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要旧杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No old magazines
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.35,0:17:20.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:20.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.72,0:17:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我不想去看医生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I don't want to go the doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我康复过来吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to help me get better, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.69,0:17:33.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:33.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当我医生好不好  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like to be my doctor, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然朋友还能干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What else are friends for?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.37,0:17:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来必须要把这些洞堵住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It appears as though we'll have to plug up these holes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该就能成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This ought to do the trick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.96,0:17:52.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:52.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Voilà
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.92,0:17:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒服点了没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feel better?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  我缩小了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help, I'm shrinking
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.85,0:18:04.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:04.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你不要伤害我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, don't hurt me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡没了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No bubbles
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你的治疗有效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, your treatment is working
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.77,0:18:10.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:10.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照这样下去  我马上就能被治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At this rate I'll be cured in no time
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该要打电话找珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm going to call Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫她不用过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and tell her not to come
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  派大星医生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Dr. Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.07,0:18:22.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别人都说我成事不足败事有余呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:22.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And they said I'd never make anything out of myself
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.42,0:18:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我手指太大  不方便按按钮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My fingers are too big for the buttons
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.92,0:18:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星医生  能帮我打给珊迪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dr. Patrick, could you call Sandy for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  海绵宝宝病人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, patient SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hiya, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我代表我病人海绵宝宝给你打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm calling on behalf of my patient, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在送他去医院的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way over to take him to the hospital
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那玩意再也用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That will no longer be required
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他今天由我来照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He is in my care as of today
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就过来瞧一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm coming over to take a look
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到这来会快得不得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be over there faster
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than a barefoot jackrabbit on a hot
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对  不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, the rabbit
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别来烦我  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't bother, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, quick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's coming
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须确认你已经康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to make sure you're well
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然她就会带你去看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or she'll take you to the doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准碰我  我无菌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me, I'm sterile
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手术刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scalpel, please
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(501.126,649.25)}海花生酱
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒服点没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒服点了没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Felling better yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不太行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not really
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.14,0:19:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,think so
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.82,0:19:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒服点没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.15,0:19:40.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:40.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about now?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.32,0:19:41.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:41.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about now?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.92,0:19:52.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:52.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有人在家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no one home
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.05,0:19:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  把这扇门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you open this door
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  有时候我就是搞不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, sometimes I just don't understand you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  海绵宝宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick, where's SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他这会儿不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not here at the moment
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.39,0:20:13.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请在哔声后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:13.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please leave a message after the beep
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, now, tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么时候开始有两座房子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since when do you have two houses?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.65,0:20:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从我没地方放东西那会开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since I ran out of space to put my stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.03,0:20:23.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:23.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家房子什么时候开始长脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since when does your house have feet?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我家房车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my mobile home
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hiya, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来泥土疗法很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The dirt therapy seems to be working just fine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  海绵宝宝必须要去看真医生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, SpongeBob has to see a real doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用不着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, he doesn't
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把他照顾得可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm taking good care of him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给人家瞧瞧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show her, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say "ah"
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.06,0:20:52.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:52.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他比我想的还要严重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's even worse than I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你几个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.60,0:20:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's fine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真没事  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm okay, Sandy, really
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上就带你去看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm taking you to the doctor right now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我的病人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my patient
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准带他去看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't take him to the doctor's
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别给我傻了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.71,0:21:15.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你马上就能康复过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you'll be better soon
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll save you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.42,0:21:25.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我康康康康康康复了  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:25.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ba-ba-ba-ba-ba-better, guys, really
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.18,0:21:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看你干的什么好事  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now look what you've done, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I've done?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一出来事情就全乱套了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything was fine until you showed up
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.23,0:21:36.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你非法行医  迟早会被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:36.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should be arrested for impersonating a doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是个好医生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a good doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.19,0:21:38.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:38.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.98,0:21:39.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:39.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.11,0:21:40.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:40.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't stop now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.07,0:21:45.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:45.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亮晶晶的硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shiny dimes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.70,0:21:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.49,0:21:53.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:53.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快停下  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:14.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(620.694,927)}医院
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:16.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(872.173,630)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.98,0:22:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝先生  看来你得了肥皂泡病
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. SquarePants, it seems you have the suds
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.65,0:22:21.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好接受治疗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:21.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready for your treatment?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.77,0:22:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你该不会要我看旧杂志吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not going to make me read old magazines, are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.32,0:22:27.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会的  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, silly
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.57,0:22:29.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要接受海绵疗法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:29.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you get the sponge treatment
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.28,0:22:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汉斯快来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hans
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.92,0:22:40.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:40.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.84,0:22:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This tickles
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.51,0:22:47.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又能闻到味了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:47.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can smell again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.26,0:22:53.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:53.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.89,0:22:57.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:57.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel as good as new
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱医生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love the doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.73,0:23:01.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的棒棒糖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:01.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your lollipop
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.98,0:23:07.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有棒棒糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:07.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A lollipop?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.49,0:23:14.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医生  我也得肥皂泡病了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:14.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doc, I got the suds, too
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  派大星医生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, Dr. Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.33,0:23:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们给你准备了特殊的疗法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have a special treatment for you
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.42,0:23:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.55,0:23:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That hurts
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.17,0:23:29.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:29.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事情好像不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This doesn't seem right
